{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Plan: 1. Refactor the existing export-asset persistence into a general session-asset model that can represent draft snapshots, composition/audio segments, final audio, and docx/text artifacts. 2. Add a repository and service layer for cr...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_23", "text": "Plan:\n1. Refactor the existing export-asset persistence into a general session-asset model that can represent draft snapshots, composition/audio segments, final audio, and docx/text artifacts.\n2. Add a repository and service layer for creating asset records, marking them ready or failed, and listing session/downloadable artifacts from the database.\n3. Update current session aggregate code and tests to use the generalized asset records, then run migrations/tests to verify both schema and behavior.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 49, "prompt_index": 17, "prompt_name": "16 \u2014 Asset Metadata and File Records", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T23:56:32-07:00"}
